  "description": "<p>Net Weight: 25ml</p><p>Functions: Lightweight, Hydrating&nbsp;</p><p>Suggested Usage:<br/>-Pump one to two shots of primer onto the back of your hand.<br/>-Blend a thin layer onto clean skin before makeup application.<br/>-Let the formula set for one minute to absorb and activate grip for all-day hold.<br/>-Layer foundation and other makeup on top for a smooth application that lasts all day, or wear alone for a glassy, hydrated, fresh face.<br/>-Pro Tip: To prevent pilling, let skincare and suncreen fully absorb before primer application.</p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"https://cc-west-usa.oss-us-west-1.aliyuncs.com/cbd20f56-6f7d-4ddb-975f-d8fa2edef25c.png\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-src=\"https://cc-west-usa.oss-us-west-1.aliyuncs.com/17555616/1957730514731536384.jpg\" data-key=\"1\" data-uploadossfail=\"false\"/><img src=\"https://cc-west-usa.oss-us-west-1.aliyuncs.com/9fcc4bac-3d41-44b4-b6da-d74926d2f85a.png\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-src=\"https://cc-west-usa.oss-us-west-1.aliyuncs.com/17555616/1957730515142578176.jpg\" data-key=\"2\" data-uploadossfail=\"false\"/><img src=\"https://cc-west-usa.oss-us-west-1.aliyuncs.com/2d468e94-b740-4e69-9b71-3c98d18f33cd.png\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-src=\"https://cc-west-usa.oss-us-west-1.aliyuncs.com/17555616/1957730515356487680.jpg\" data-key=\"3\" data-uploadossfail=\"false\"/><img src=\"https://cc-west-usa.oss-us-west-1.aliyuncs.com/1f880cdc-587a-4a55-b568-f11a1e145f31.png\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-src=\"https://cc-west-usa.oss-us-west-1.aliyuncs.com/17555616/1957730519366242304.jpg\" data-key=\"4\" data-uploadossfail=\"false\"/><img src=\"https://cc-west-usa.oss-us-west-1.aliyuncs.com/2c9972f2-1951-4aed-9de7-f7fb73700b3a.png\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-src=\"https://cc-west-usa.oss-us-west-1.aliyuncs.com/17555616/1957730519697592320.jpg\" data-k